<bibRefCitation author="Schweger, S. &amp; Melika, G. &amp; Tang, C. - T. &amp; Bihari, P. &amp; Bozso, M. &amp; Stone, G. N. &amp; Nicholls, J. A. &amp; Penzes, Z." box="[952,1219,1101,1128]" pageId="41" pageNumber="42" pagination="451 - 497" refId="ref52498" refString="Schweger, S., Melika, G., Tang, C. - T., Bihari, P., Bozso, M., Stone, G. N., Nicholls, J. A. &amp; Penzes, Z. (2015 a) New species of cynipid inquilines of the genus Synergus (Hymenoptera: Cynipidae: Synergini) from the Eastern Palaearctic. Zootaxa, 3999 (4), 451 - 497. https: // doi. org / 10.11646 / zootaxa. 3999.4.1" type="journal article" year="2015">
